# Intuit Design System - FontName Token Library

## Primitive FontName Tokens (DO NOT USE DIRECTLY IN PLUGINS)

- `--font-name-avenir`: Avenir Next forINTUIT
- `--font-name-avenir-variable`: AvenirNextForINTUITVar
- `--font-name-graphik`: Graphik
- `--font-name-means`: Means
- `--font-name-national`: National2

## Semantic FontName Tokens (USE THESE IN PLUGINS)

### Name
- `--font-name-body`: --font-name-avenir /* For body text styles. Do not use these in atom sized UI components instead use font-component tokens. */
- `--font-name-component`: --font-name-avenir /* For component text styles */
- `--font-name-display`: --font-name-avenir /* For display text styles */
- `--font-name-heading`: --font-name-avenir /* For heading text styles */
- `--font-name-mega`: --font-name-avenir /* For mega text styles */
